1
00:00:07,417 --> 00:00:09,750
Katara: WATER...

2
00:00:09,792 --> 00:00:11,583
EARTH...

3
00:00:11,625 --> 00:00:13,750
FIRE...

4
00:00:13,792 --> 00:00:16,166
AIR...

5
00:00:16,208 --> 00:00:20,291
LONG AGO, THE 4 NATIONS
LIVED TOGETHER IN HARMONY.

6
00:00:20,333 --> 00:00:24,542
THEN, EVERYTHING CHANGED
WHEN THE FIRE NATION ATTACKED.

7
00:00:24,583 --> 00:00:27,250
ONLY THE AVATAR,
MASTER OF ALL 4 ELEMENTS,

8
00:00:27,291 --> 00:00:28,959
COULD STOP THEM.

9
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,375
BUT WHEN THE WORLD
NEEDED HIM MOST,

10
00:00:30,417 --> 00:00:32,125
HE VANISHED.

11
00:00:32,166 --> 00:00:34,166
A HUNDRED YEARS PASSED,
AND MY BROTHER AND I

12
00:00:34,208 --> 00:00:37,959
DISCOVERED THE NEW AVATAR,
AN AIRBENDER NAMED AANG.

13
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:40,000
AND ALTHOUGH HIS AIRBENDING
SKILLS ARE GREAT,

14
00:00:40,041 --> 00:00:43,959
HE HAS A LOT TO LEARN BEFORE
HE'S READY TO SAVE ANYONE.

15
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:47,125
BUT I BELIEVE AANG
CAN SAVE THE WORLD.

16
00:00:55,375 --> 00:00:57,458
Katara, voice-over:
WHEN THE AVATAR DIES,

17
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:59,792
HE'S REINCARNATED
INTO THE NEXT NATION
IN THE CYCLE.

18
00:00:59,834 --> 00:01:01,667
Aang: THAT'S AVATAR ROKU,

19
00:01:01,709 --> 00:01:03,041
THE AVATAR BEFORE ME.

20
00:01:03,083 --> 00:01:06,625
WHEN YOU ARE READY,
HE WILL REVEAL
HIMSELF TO YOU.

21
00:01:06,667 --> 00:01:09,875
I LOST MY MOTHER
IN A FIRE NATION RAID.

22
00:01:09,917 --> 00:01:11,834
THIS NECKLACE IS ALL I
HAVE LEFT OF HER.

23
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:20,667
THE WORLD HAS CHANGED
IN THE HUNDRED YEARS
YOU'VE BEEN GONE.

24
00:01:20,709 --> 00:01:22,959
IT'S THE DUTY
OF THE AVATAR TO
RESTORE BALANCE

25
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:26,208
TO THE WORLD
BY DEFEATING
FIRE LORD OZAI.

26
00:01:26,250 --> 00:01:29,458
SEND WORD TO
THE FIRE LORD IMMEDIATELY.

27
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:31,667
THE AVATAR
HAS RETURNED.

28
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,083
[SQUAWK]

29
00:01:48,375 --> 00:01:50,417
[APPA GROWLING]

30
00:01:52,208 --> 00:01:54,709
Katara: THOSE CLOUDS
LOOK SO SOFT, DON'T THEY?

31
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:56,709
LIKE YOU COULD
JUST JUMP DOWN

32
00:01:56,750 --> 00:01:59,083
AND YOU'D LAND
IN A BIG, SOFT,
COTTONY HEAP.

33
00:01:59,125 --> 00:02:01,125
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
GIVE IT A TRY.

34
00:02:01,166 --> 00:02:02,834
YOU'RE HILARIOUS.

35
00:02:02,875 --> 00:02:03,750
I'LL TRY IT!

36
00:02:03,792 --> 00:02:04,667
HA HA HA!

37
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:08,792
YEAH!

38
00:02:14,250 --> 00:02:15,709
TURNS OUT, CLOUDS
ARE MADE OF WATER.

39
00:02:21,250 --> 00:02:23,125
HEY, WHAT IS THAT?

40
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,250
IT'S LIKE A SCAR.

41
00:02:33,458 --> 00:02:34,917
Sokka: LISTEN.

42
00:02:34,959 --> 00:02:37,333
IT'S SO QUIET.

43
00:02:37,375 --> 00:02:38,792
THERE'S NO LIFE
ANYWHERE.

44
00:02:38,834 --> 00:02:41,500
AANG, ARE YOU OK?

45
00:02:41,542 --> 00:02:42,917
FIRE NATION!

46
00:02:42,959 --> 00:02:44,667
THOSE EVIL SAVAGES
MAKE ME SICK.

47
00:02:44,709 --> 00:02:45,792
THEY HAVE
NO RESPECT FOR--

48
00:02:45,834 --> 00:02:47,500
SHH.

49
00:02:47,542 --> 00:02:48,875
WHAT, I'M NOT
ALLOWED TO BE ANGRY?

50
00:02:51,667 --> 00:02:52,417
[SIGH]

51
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,917
WHY WOULD ANYONE DO THIS?

52
00:02:55,959 --> 00:02:58,166
HOW COULD I LET THIS HAPPEN?

53
00:02:58,208 --> 00:03:00,625
AANG, YOU DIDN'T
LET THIS HAPPEN.

54
00:03:00,667 --> 00:03:02,291
IT HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH YOU.

55
00:03:02,333 --> 00:03:03,875
YES, IT DOES.

56
00:03:03,917 --> 00:03:06,583
IT'S THE AVATAR'S JOB
TO PROTECT NATURE,

57
00:03:06,625 --> 00:03:08,291
BUT I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO DO MY JOB.

58
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:10,333
THAT'S WHY WE'RE GOING
TO THE NORTH POLE--

59
00:03:10,375 --> 00:03:11,792
TO FIND YOU
A TEACHER.

60
00:03:11,834 --> 00:03:14,208
YEAH. A WATERBENDING TEACHER.

61
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:16,750
BUT THERE'S NO ONE
WHO CAN TEACH ME HOW
TO BE THE AVATAR.

62
00:03:16,792 --> 00:03:19,625
MONK GYATSU SAID THAT
AVATAR ROKU WOULD HELP ME.

63
00:03:19,667 --> 00:03:21,834
THE AVATAR
BEFORE YOU?

64
00:03:21,875 --> 00:03:23,542
HE DIED
OVER A HUNDRED
YEARS AGO.

65
00:03:23,583 --> 00:03:24,959
HOW ARE YOU
SUPPOSED TO TALK
TO HIM?

66
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,166
I DON'T KNOW.

67
00:03:27,208 --> 00:03:28,834
[PURRING]

68
00:03:31,625 --> 00:03:33,083
UNCLE,
IT'S TIME TO LEAVE.

69
00:03:33,125 --> 00:03:36,083
WHERE ARE YOU?
UNCLE IROH!

70
00:03:36,125 --> 00:03:37,834
OVER HERE.

71
00:03:37,875 --> 00:03:38,875
UNCLE?

72
00:03:38,917 --> 00:03:40,625
WE NEED TO MOVE ON.

73
00:03:40,667 --> 00:03:42,250
WE'RE CLOSING IN
ON THE AVATAR'S
TRAIL,

74
00:03:42,291 --> 00:03:44,625
AND I DON'T
WANT TO LOSE HIM.

75
00:03:44,667 --> 00:03:47,375
YOU LOOK TIRED,
PRINCE ZUKO.

76
00:03:47,417 --> 00:03:50,667
WHY DON'T YOU JOIN ME
IN THESE HOT SPRINGS

77
00:03:50,709 --> 00:03:53,583
AND SOAK AWAY
YOUR TROUBLES?

78
00:03:53,625 --> 00:03:55,709
MY TROUBLES CANNOT
BE SOAKED AWAY.

79
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:57,583
IT'S TIME TO GO!

80
00:03:57,625 --> 00:03:59,917
YOU SHOULD TAKE
YOUR TEACHER'S ADVICE

81
00:03:59,959 --> 00:04:02,375
AND RELAX A LITTLE.

82
00:04:02,417 --> 00:04:05,625
THE TEMPERATURE'S
JUST RIGHT.

83
00:04:05,667 --> 00:04:07,875
I HEATED IT MYSELF.

84
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:13,041
ENOUGH. WE NEED
TO LEAVE NOW.

85
00:04:13,083 --> 00:04:14,166
GET OUT
OF THE WATER!

86
00:04:14,208 --> 00:04:15,709
VERY WELL.

87
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:17,250
ON SECOND THOUGHT,

88
00:04:17,291 --> 00:04:19,041
WHY DON'T YOU TAKE
ANOTHER FEW MINUTES?

89
00:04:19,083 --> 00:04:20,792
BUT BE BACK
AT THE SHIP
IN HALF AN HOUR,

90
00:04:20,834 --> 00:04:22,083
OR I'M LEAVING
WITHOUT YOU.

91
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:23,959
AHH.

92
00:04:26,125 --> 00:04:27,750
Katara: HEY, AANG.

93
00:04:27,792 --> 00:04:29,375
ARE YOU READY
TO BE CHEERED UP?

94
00:04:29,417 --> 00:04:32,083
NO.
OW!

95
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:34,166
HEY, HOW IS THAT
CHEERING ME UP?

96
00:04:34,208 --> 00:04:35,250
[CHUCKLING]

97
00:04:35,291 --> 00:04:36,583
CHEERED ME UP.

98
00:04:36,625 --> 00:04:37,959
OW!

99
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,667
YEAH, I PROBABLY
DESERVED THAT.

100
00:04:40,709 --> 00:04:43,709
THESE ACORNS
ARE EVERYWHERE, AANG.

101
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:46,208
THAT MEANS THE FOREST
WILL GROW BACK.

102
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:48,667
EVERY ONE OF THESE
WILL BE A TALL
OAK TREE SOMEDAY,

103
00:04:48,709 --> 00:04:50,333
AND ALL THE BIRDS
AND ANIMALS

104
00:04:50,375 --> 00:04:51,709
THAT LIVED HERE
WILL COME BACK.

105
00:04:54,667 --> 00:04:56,709
THANKS, KATARA.

106
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:57,417
[GASP]

107
00:04:59,125 --> 00:05:01,083
Sokka: HEY,
WHO ARE YOU?

108
00:05:01,125 --> 00:05:03,500
WHEN I SAW
THE FLYING BISON,

109
00:05:03,542 --> 00:05:05,208
I THOUGHT
IT WAS IMPOSSIBLE,

110
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:07,750
BUT THOSE MARKINGS...

111
00:05:07,792 --> 00:05:10,125
ARE YOU THE AVATAR,
CHILD?

112
00:05:13,166 --> 00:05:15,792
MY VILLAGE
DESPERATELY NEEDS
YOUR HELP.

113
00:05:29,417 --> 00:05:33,000
THIS YOUNG PERSON
IS THE AVATAR.

114
00:05:33,041 --> 00:05:36,500
SO THE RUMORS
OF YOUR RETURN ARE TRUE.

115
00:05:36,542 --> 00:05:38,458
IT IS THE GREATEST HONOR
OF A LIFETIME

116
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,000
TO BE IN YOUR PRESENCE.

117
00:05:40,041 --> 00:05:41,709
NICE TO MEET YOU,
TOO.

118
00:05:43,709 --> 00:05:46,500
SO, IS THERE SOMETHING
I CAN HELP YOU WITH?

119
00:05:46,542 --> 00:05:48,667
I'M NOT SURE.

120
00:05:48,709 --> 00:05:50,250
OUR VILLAGE
IS IN CRISIS.

121
00:05:50,291 --> 00:05:52,792
HE'S OUR ONLY HOPE.

122
00:05:52,834 --> 00:05:55,667
FOR THE LAST FEW DAYS
AT SUNSET,

123
00:05:55,709 --> 00:05:58,875
A SPIRIT MONSTER COMES
AND ATTACKS OUR VILLAGE.

124
00:05:58,917 --> 00:06:01,000
HE IS HEI BAI,

125
00:06:01,041 --> 00:06:03,625
THE BLACK AND WHITE SPIRIT.

126
00:06:03,667 --> 00:06:05,166
WHY IS IT
ATTACKING YOU?

127
00:06:05,208 --> 00:06:06,667
WE DO NOT KNOW.

128
00:06:06,709 --> 00:06:08,625
BUT EACH
OF THE LAST 3 NIGHTS,

129
00:06:08,667 --> 00:06:10,750
HE HAS ABDUCTED
ONE OF OUR OWN.

130
00:06:10,792 --> 00:06:12,291
WE ARE ESPECIALLY
FEARFUL

131
00:06:12,333 --> 00:06:14,458
BECAUSE THE WINTER
SOLSTICE DRAWS NEAR.

132
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:15,959
WHAT HAPPENS THEN?

133
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,083
AS THE SOLSTICE
APPROACHES,

134
00:06:18,125 --> 00:06:20,709
THE NATURAL WORLD
AND THE SPIRIT WORLD

135
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,625
GROW CLOSER
AND CLOSER,

136
00:06:22,667 --> 00:06:24,083
UNTIL THE LINE
BETWEEN THEM

137
00:06:24,125 --> 00:06:26,834
IS BLURRED COMPLETELY.

138
00:06:26,875 --> 00:06:30,500
HEI BAI IS ALREADY
CAUSING DEVASTATION
AND DESTRUCTION.

139
00:06:30,542 --> 00:06:32,208
ONCE THE SOLSTICE
IS HERE,

140
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:34,750
THERE IS NO TELLING
WHAT WILL HAPPEN.

141
00:06:34,792 --> 00:06:37,542
SO WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO EXACTLY?

142
00:06:37,583 --> 00:06:39,375
WHO BETTER
TO RESOLVE A CRISIS

143
00:06:39,417 --> 00:06:42,125
BETWEEN OUR WORLD
AND THE SPIRIT WORLD

144
00:06:42,166 --> 00:06:44,709
THAN THE AVATAR
HIMSELF?

145
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,208
YOU ARE
THE GREAT BRIDGE

146
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:48,583
BETWEEN MAN
AND SPIRITS.

147
00:06:48,625 --> 00:06:51,125
RIGHT. THAT'S ME.

148
00:06:51,166 --> 00:06:52,917
HEY,
GREAT BRIDGE GUY.

149
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:54,834
CAN I TALK
TO YOU OVER HERE
FOR A SECOND?

150
00:06:56,792 --> 00:06:59,709
AANG, YOU SEEM
A LITTLE UNSURE
ABOUT ALL THIS.

151
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:02,166
YEAH. THAT MIGHT BE
BECAUSE I DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING AT ALL

152
00:07:02,208 --> 00:07:03,667
ABOUT THE SPIRIT
WORLD.

153
00:07:05,125 --> 00:07:07,625
IT'S NOT LIKE
THERE'S SOMEONE TO
TEACH ME THIS STUFF.

154
00:07:07,667 --> 00:07:09,959
SO, CAN YOU HELP
THESE PEOPLE?

155
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,709
I HAVE TO TRY,
DON'T I?

156
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,375
MAYBE WHATEVER
I HAVE TO DO
WILL JUST...

157
00:07:14,417 --> 00:07:15,583
COME TO ME.

158
00:07:15,625 --> 00:07:17,417
[PURRING]

159
00:07:17,458 --> 00:07:20,333
I THINK YOU
CAN DO IT, AANG.

160
00:07:20,375 --> 00:07:22,250
YEAH.

161
00:07:22,291 --> 00:07:24,291
WE'RE ALL GONNA
GET EATEN BY
A SPIRIT MONSTER.

162
00:07:29,917 --> 00:07:32,750
[SNORING]

163
00:07:32,792 --> 00:07:33,959
[RUSTLING]

164
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,166
WHO'S THERE?

165
00:07:36,208 --> 00:07:37,250
[SQUEAKING]

166
00:07:37,291 --> 00:07:39,166
A MEADOW VOLE.

167
00:07:39,208 --> 00:07:41,333
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN.

168
00:07:41,375 --> 00:07:44,166
YOU STARTLED ME,
LITTLE ONE.

169
00:07:44,208 --> 00:07:45,959
[SIGH]

170
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:49,625
SEEMS I DOZED OFF AND MISSED
MY NEPHEW'S DEADLINE,

171
00:07:49,667 --> 00:07:52,792
BUT IT WAS A VERY SWEET NAP.

172
00:07:52,834 --> 00:07:54,917
[SQUEAKING]

173
00:07:57,208 --> 00:07:59,291
[RUMBLING]

174
00:08:01,583 --> 00:08:02,208
UHH!

175
00:08:05,125 --> 00:08:06,834
HE'S A FIRE NATION
SOLDIER.

176
00:08:06,875 --> 00:08:08,917
HE'S NO
ORDINARY SOLDIER.

177
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:10,917
THIS IS
THE FIRE LORD'S
BROTHER.

178
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,583
THE DRAGON
OF THE WEST--

179
00:08:12,625 --> 00:08:15,458
THE ONCE GREAT
GENERAL IROH.

180
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,250
BUT NOW,
HE'S OUR PRISONER.

181
00:08:29,792 --> 00:08:32,750
HELLO? SPIRIT?
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

182
00:08:32,792 --> 00:08:35,291
THIS IS THE AVATAR SPEAKING.

183
00:08:35,333 --> 00:08:38,166
I'M HERE TO TRY
TO HELP STUFF.

184
00:08:38,208 --> 00:08:39,709
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

185
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,417
WE CAN'T SIT HERE
AND COWER WHILE AANG

186
00:08:41,458 --> 00:08:43,250
WAITS FOR SOME
MONSTER TO SHOW UP.

187
00:08:43,291 --> 00:08:45,792
IF ANYONE CAN SAVE US,
HE CAN.

188
00:08:45,834 --> 00:08:48,291
HE STILL SHOULDN'T
HAVE TO FACE THIS
ALONE.

189
00:08:54,458 --> 00:08:55,667
THE SUN IS SET.

190
00:08:55,709 --> 00:08:58,542
WHERE ARE YOU, HEI BAI?

191
00:08:58,583 --> 00:09:01,417
WELL, SPIRIT, UH,

192
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:02,959
I HEREBY ASK YOU

193
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,709
TO PLEASE LEAVE
THIS VILLAGE IN PEACE.

194
00:09:08,875 --> 00:09:13,625
OK. WELL, I GUESS
THAT'S SETTLED, THEN.

195
00:09:13,667 --> 00:09:15,083
[VOICES WHISPERING]

196
00:09:32,792 --> 00:09:36,583
YOU MUST BE
THE HEI BAI SPIRIT.
MY NAME IS--

197
00:09:36,625 --> 00:09:37,667
[ROARS]

198
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,000
MY NAME IS AANG.
I'M THE AVATAR,

199
00:09:44,041 --> 00:09:45,583
AND I WOULD LIKE TO HELP.

200
00:09:45,625 --> 00:09:46,291
HEY, WAIT UP!

201
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,166
[ROARING]

202
00:09:57,917 --> 00:09:58,667
UH...

203
00:10:00,208 --> 00:10:02,542
THE AVATAR'S
METHODS ARE...

204
00:10:02,583 --> 00:10:04,000
UNUSUAL.

205
00:10:04,041 --> 00:10:05,208
IT DOESN'T SEEM
TOO INTERESTED

206
00:10:05,250 --> 00:10:06,625
IN WHAT HE'S SAYING.

207
00:10:06,667 --> 00:10:08,834
MAYBE WE SHOULD
GO HELP HIM.

208
00:10:08,875 --> 00:10:12,333
NO. ONLY THE AVATAR
STANDS A CHANCE
AGAINST THE HEI BAI.

209
00:10:12,375 --> 00:10:15,083
AANG WILL FIGURE OUT
THE RIGHT THING
TO DO, SOKKA.

210
00:10:18,291 --> 00:10:21,625
PLEASE, WOULD YOU STOP
DESTROYING THINGS AND LISTEN?

211
00:10:21,667 --> 00:10:24,208
I'M JUST TRYING
TO DO MY JOB
AS SPIRIT BRIDGE.

212
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:25,625
EXCUSE ME.

213
00:10:25,667 --> 00:10:28,125
WOULD YOU PLEASE
TURN AROUND?

214
00:10:28,166 --> 00:10:30,166
I COMMAND YOU
TO TURN AROUND NOW!

215
00:10:31,792 --> 00:10:32,709
UHH!

216
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,458
THAT'S IT.
HE NEEDS HELP.

217
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:38,125
SOKKA! WAIT!

218
00:10:40,041 --> 00:10:41,750
Leader:
IT'S NOT SAFE.

219
00:10:41,792 --> 00:10:43,709
HEI BAI. OVER HERE!

220
00:10:47,709 --> 00:10:49,417
SOKKA! GO BACK!

221
00:10:49,458 --> 00:10:51,250
WE'LL FIGHT HIM
TOGETHER, AANG.

222
00:10:51,291 --> 00:10:53,250
I DON'T WANT TO
FIGHT HIM UNLESS I--

223
00:10:59,583 --> 00:11:00,709
SOKKA!

224
00:11:07,834 --> 00:11:08,792
UNCLE.

225
00:11:08,834 --> 00:11:10,750
UNCLE, WHERE ARE YOU?

226
00:11:10,792 --> 00:11:12,625
SIR, MAYBE HE THOUGHT
YOU LEFT WITHOUT HIM.

227
00:11:12,667 --> 00:11:15,041
SOMETHING'S NOT RIGHT HERE.

228
00:11:15,083 --> 00:11:17,291
THAT PILE OF ROCKS.

229
00:11:17,333 --> 00:11:19,542
IT LOOKS LIKE
THERE'S BEEN
A LANDSLIDE, SIR.

230
00:11:19,583 --> 00:11:21,750
LAND DOESN'T SLIDE UPHILL.

231
00:11:21,792 --> 00:11:24,709
THOSE ROCKS
DIDN'T MOVE NATURALLY.

232
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:26,625
MY UNCLE'S BEEN CAPTURED
BY EARTHBENDERS.

233
00:11:32,583 --> 00:11:33,709
[GASPING]

234
00:11:37,709 --> 00:11:39,834
Sokka: AANG!
OVER HERE!

235
00:11:47,542 --> 00:11:48,500
HELP!

236
00:11:48,542 --> 00:11:49,542
HANG ON, SOKKA!

237
00:11:52,041 --> 00:11:54,750
[GRUNTING]

238
00:11:57,583 --> 00:11:58,625
AAH!

239
00:11:58,667 --> 00:11:59,750
UHH!

240
00:12:07,875 --> 00:12:08,709
SOKKA!

241
00:12:11,792 --> 00:12:13,166
I'VE FAILED.

242
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:29,583
WHERE ARE YOU
TAKING ME?

243
00:12:29,625 --> 00:12:31,583
WE'RE TAKING YOU
TO FACE JUSTICE.

244
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:32,834
RIGHT.

245
00:12:32,875 --> 00:12:35,208
BUT WHERE,
SPECIFICALLY?

246
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:37,667
A PLACE YOU'RE
QUITE FAMILIAR WITH,
ACTUALLY.

247
00:12:37,709 --> 00:12:41,709
YOU ONCE LAID SIEGE
TO IT FOR 600 DAYS,

248
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:43,792
BUT IT WOULD NOT
YIELD TO YOU.

249
00:12:43,834 --> 00:12:48,125
AH, THE GREAT CITY
OF BA SING SE.

250
00:12:48,166 --> 00:12:50,625
IT WAS GREATER
THAN YOU WERE,
APPARENTLY.

251
00:12:50,667 --> 00:12:54,792
I ACKNOWLEDGE MY DEFEAT
AT BA SING SE.

252
00:12:54,834 --> 00:12:57,709
AFTER 600 DAYS
AWAY FROM HOME,

253
00:12:57,750 --> 00:13:01,875
MY MEN WERE TIRED,
AND I WAS TIRED.

254
00:13:01,917 --> 00:13:04,709
[YAWN]

255
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:06,875
AND I'M STILL TIRED.

256
00:13:27,625 --> 00:13:29,375
I'M SURE
THEY'LL BE BACK.

257
00:13:29,417 --> 00:13:30,041
I KNOW.

258
00:13:33,125 --> 00:13:35,333
YOU SHOULD
GET SOME REST.

259
00:13:35,375 --> 00:13:36,667
EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE OK.

260
00:13:38,625 --> 00:13:41,166
YOUR BROTHER
IS IN GOOD HANDS.

261
00:13:41,208 --> 00:13:42,875
I WOULD BE SHOCKED

262
00:13:42,917 --> 00:13:45,458
IF THE AVATAR
RETURNED
WITHOUT HIM.

263
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:48,417
KATARA?
KATARA, I LOST HIM.

264
00:13:51,041 --> 00:13:53,625
THE SUN IS RISING.

265
00:13:53,667 --> 00:13:56,333
PERHAPS HE WILL
RETURN SOON.

266
00:13:56,375 --> 00:13:58,458
WHAT? NO.
I'M RIGHT HERE.

267
00:13:58,500 --> 00:13:59,583
GRR!

268
00:13:59,625 --> 00:14:00,917
[GRUNTING]

269
00:14:07,375 --> 00:14:09,000
I'M IN THE SPIRIT WORLD.

270
00:14:17,667 --> 00:14:19,959
UGH. YEP,
THAT'S UNCLE IROH.

271
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:26,834
Aang: I'LL FIGURE
THIS OUT, KATARA.
I PROMISE.

272
00:14:26,875 --> 00:14:28,542
LIKE THEY SAID,
I'M THE BRIDGE

273
00:14:28,583 --> 00:14:30,500
BETWEEN THE WORLDS,
RIGHT?

274
00:14:30,542 --> 00:14:33,458
ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS FIGURE OUT
WHAT I HAVE TO DO,

275
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:34,959
BUT ONCE I DO THAT,
NO PROBLEM.

276
00:14:36,875 --> 00:14:37,792
[GROWLING]

277
00:14:37,834 --> 00:14:38,959
APPA. HEY, BUDDY.
I'M RIGHT HERE.

278
00:14:41,458 --> 00:14:44,625
BUT I GUESS YOU
CAN'T SEE ME, EITHER.

279
00:14:44,667 --> 00:14:46,166
[DULL ROAR]

280
00:14:46,208 --> 00:14:48,125
IT'S OK, APPA.
DON'T WORRY.

281
00:14:48,166 --> 00:14:50,250
I'M SURE THEY'RE
ON THEIR WAY BACK.

282
00:14:50,291 --> 00:14:52,291
I BET THEY EVEN
FOUND YOU A BUNCH
OF MOON PEACHES,

283
00:14:52,333 --> 00:14:53,208
FOR A TREAT.

284
00:14:55,875 --> 00:14:58,417
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?

285
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:00,625
AVATAR ROKU,
HOW CAN I TALK TO YOU?

286
00:15:03,667 --> 00:15:04,291
SOKKA?

287
00:15:09,166 --> 00:15:10,750
[GROWLING]

288
00:15:10,792 --> 00:15:13,250
THAT'S DEFINITELY NOT SOKKA.

289
00:15:15,375 --> 00:15:16,000
UHH!

290
00:15:22,458 --> 00:15:24,000
WHAT?

291
00:15:24,041 --> 00:15:26,500
I CAN'T AIRBEND
IN THE SPIRIT WORLD.

292
00:15:29,625 --> 00:15:30,583
[GROWLING]

293
00:15:35,834 --> 00:15:37,125
[GROWLING]

294
00:15:42,083 --> 00:15:44,125
YOU DON'T KNOW WHERE
SOKKA IS, DO YOU?

295
00:15:47,166 --> 00:15:47,875
[WHIMPERING]

296
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:57,625
YOU'RE AVATAR ROKU'S
ANIMAL GUIDE,

297
00:15:57,667 --> 00:15:59,375
LIKE APPA IS TO ME.

298
00:15:59,417 --> 00:16:01,834
I NEED TO SAVE MY FRIEND,
AND I DON'T KNOW HOW.

299
00:16:01,875 --> 00:16:03,834
IS THERE SOME WAY FOR ME
TO TALK TO ROKU?

300
00:16:08,792 --> 00:16:10,291
I'LL BE BACK, KATARA.

301
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:13,250
TAKE ME TO ROKU.

302
00:16:24,709 --> 00:16:25,333
[GASP]

303
00:16:28,792 --> 00:16:30,000
OH.

304
00:16:30,041 --> 00:16:31,917
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

305
00:16:31,959 --> 00:16:33,625
NOTHING.

306
00:16:33,667 --> 00:16:37,750
ACTUALLY, THERE IS
A BIT OF A PROBLEM.

307
00:16:37,792 --> 00:16:40,542
MY OLD JOINTS
ARE FEELING SORE
AND ACHY,

308
00:16:40,583 --> 00:16:43,083
AND THESE SHACKLES
ARE TOO LOOSE.

309
00:16:43,125 --> 00:16:44,792
TOO LOOSE?

310
00:16:44,834 --> 00:16:46,750
THAT'S RIGHT.
THE CUFFS ARE LOOSE,

311
00:16:46,792 --> 00:16:49,917
AND THEY JANGLE AROUND
AND BUMP MY WRISTS.

312
00:16:49,959 --> 00:16:52,667
IT WOULD HELP ME
IF YOU WOULD TIGHTEN THEM

313
00:16:52,709 --> 00:16:55,041
SO THEY WOULDN'T
SHAKE AROUND SO MUCH.

314
00:16:55,083 --> 00:16:56,959
VERY WELL.

315
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,458
CORPORAL, TIGHTEN
THE PRISONER'S
HANDCUFFS.

316
00:17:04,709 --> 00:17:07,333
AAH!

317
00:17:07,375 --> 00:17:08,166
AAH!

318
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:11,500
AAH!

319
00:17:26,208 --> 00:17:27,792
Aang: HEY!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

320
00:17:27,834 --> 00:17:29,709
AAH!

321
00:17:35,834 --> 00:17:37,291
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

322
00:17:37,333 --> 00:17:39,000
THIS IS JUST A STATUE
OF ROKU.

323
00:17:48,875 --> 00:17:51,083
IS THAT WHAT ROKU
WANTS TO TALK TO ME ABOUT?

324
00:17:51,125 --> 00:17:52,917
A COMET?

325
00:17:52,959 --> 00:17:55,333
WHEN CAN I TALK TO HIM?

326
00:17:55,375 --> 00:17:56,000
[GROWLING]

327
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:24,208
IT'S A CALENDAR,

328
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:27,208
AND THE LIGHT WILL REACH ROKU
ON THE SOLSTICE.

329
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:29,500
SO THAT'S WHEN I'LL BE
ABLE TO SPEAK TO ROKU?

330
00:18:29,542 --> 00:18:31,041
[GROWLING]

331
00:18:31,083 --> 00:18:33,458
BUT I CAN'T WAIT THAT LONG.

332
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,834
I NEED TO SAVE SOKKA NOW!

333
00:18:37,625 --> 00:18:38,750
UGH! UHH!

334
00:18:40,792 --> 00:18:42,000
HYAH!

335
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:51,291
HE IS TOO DANGEROUS,
CAPTAIN.

336
00:18:51,333 --> 00:18:53,125
WE CAN'T
JUST CARRY HIM
TO THE CAPITAL.

337
00:18:53,166 --> 00:18:54,834
WE HAVE TO DO
SOMETHING NOW.

338
00:18:54,875 --> 00:18:56,333
I AGREE.

339
00:18:56,375 --> 00:18:57,709
HE MUST BE DEALT WITH
IMMEDIATELY

340
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:59,709
AND SEVERELY.

341
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:00,750
PTOH!

342
00:19:03,333 --> 00:19:06,208
Katara: IT'S NO USE, APPA.
I DON'T SEE THEM ANYWHERE.

343
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:09,166
OUR BEST HOPE IS TO GO BACK
TO THE VILLAGE AND WAIT.

344
00:19:09,208 --> 00:19:10,375
[APPA GROWLS]

345
00:19:16,417 --> 00:19:17,875
THE AVATAR.

346
00:19:30,792 --> 00:19:32,834
WHOA.

347
00:19:32,875 --> 00:19:33,875
AAH!

348
00:20:02,125 --> 00:20:03,333
YOU'RE BACK!

349
00:20:05,083 --> 00:20:07,625
WHERE'S SOKKA?

350
00:20:07,667 --> 00:20:08,792
I'M NOT SURE.

351
00:20:14,583 --> 00:20:17,291
Captain: THESE DANGEROUS HANDS
MUST BE CRUSHED.

352
00:20:17,333 --> 00:20:18,750
[GRUNTING]

353
00:20:22,667 --> 00:20:23,375
HYAH!

354
00:20:26,208 --> 00:20:27,750
HYAH!

355
00:20:27,792 --> 00:20:29,959
EXCELLENT FORM,
PRINCE ZUKO.

356
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,625
YOU TAUGHT ME WELL.

357
00:20:31,667 --> 00:20:32,709
Captain:
SURRENDER YOURSELVES.

358
00:20:32,750 --> 00:20:34,625
IT'S 5 AGAINST 2.

359
00:20:34,667 --> 00:20:36,750
YOU'RE CLEARLY OUTNUMBERED.

360
00:20:36,792 --> 00:20:38,792
UH, THAT'S TRUE,

361
00:20:38,834 --> 00:20:41,792
BUT YOU ARE
CLEARLY OUTMATCHED.

362
00:20:41,834 --> 00:20:43,417
HY...AH!

363
00:20:43,458 --> 00:20:44,250
YAH!
YAH!

364
00:20:46,959 --> 00:20:48,083
HYAH! HYAH!

365
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,333
[GRUNTING]

366
00:20:53,375 --> 00:20:54,542
HYAH!

367
00:20:54,583 --> 00:20:55,208
UHH!
UHH!

368
00:21:00,792 --> 00:21:01,625
UHH!

369
00:21:01,667 --> 00:21:03,875
UHH! UHH!

370
00:21:05,875 --> 00:21:06,542
YAH!

371
00:21:09,875 --> 00:21:10,709
OH!

372
00:21:12,709 --> 00:21:15,333
[SOLDIERS GROANING]

373
00:21:18,083 --> 00:21:20,917
NOW, WOULD YOU PLEASE
PUT ON SOME CLOTHES?

374
00:21:20,959 --> 00:21:22,625
[VOICES WHISPERING]

375
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:36,291
[CHIMING]

376
00:21:41,792 --> 00:21:43,417
AAH!

377
00:21:43,458 --> 00:21:44,792
AANG!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

378
00:21:44,834 --> 00:21:46,583
RUN!

379
00:21:46,625 --> 00:21:48,041
[ROARING]

380
00:22:01,709 --> 00:22:03,500
[ROARING]

381
00:22:03,542 --> 00:22:05,709
YOU'RE THE SPIRIT
OF THIS FOREST.

382
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:07,750
NOW I UNDERSTAND.

383
00:22:07,792 --> 00:22:09,208
YOU'RE UPSET
AND ANGRY

384
00:22:09,250 --> 00:22:11,834
BECAUSE YOUR HOME
WAS BURNED DOWN.

385
00:22:11,875 --> 00:22:14,625
WHEN I SAW THE FOREST
HAD BURNED, I WAS SAD AND UPSET,

386
00:22:14,667 --> 00:22:16,333
BUT MY FRIEND
GAVE ME HOPE

387
00:22:16,375 --> 00:22:17,458
THAT THE FOREST
WOULD GROW BACK.

388
00:22:38,458 --> 00:22:39,458
SOKKA!

389
00:22:40,583 --> 00:22:42,542
WHAT HAPPENED?

390
00:22:42,583 --> 00:22:45,083
YOU WERE TRAPPED
IN THE SPIRIT WORLD
FOR 24 HOURS.

391
00:22:45,125 --> 00:22:46,709
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

392
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:48,375
LIKE I SERIOUSLY NEED
TO USE THE BATHROOM.

393
00:22:50,542 --> 00:22:52,458
THANK YOU, AVATAR.

394
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:53,917
IF ONLY THERE WERE A WAY

395
00:22:53,959 --> 00:22:55,875
TO REPAY YOU
FOR WHAT YOU'VE DONE.

396
00:22:55,917 --> 00:22:58,750
YOU COULD GIVE US
SOME SUPPLIES
AND SOME MONEY.

397
00:22:58,792 --> 00:23:00,041
SOKKA.
WHAT?

398
00:23:00,083 --> 00:23:02,208
WE NEED STUFF.

399
00:23:02,250 --> 00:23:05,917
IT WOULD BE AN HONOR
TO HELP YOU PREPARE
FOR YOUR JOURNEY.

400
00:23:05,959 --> 00:23:08,000
I'M SO PROUD
OF YOU, AANG.

401
00:23:08,041 --> 00:23:10,417
YOU FIGURED OUT WHAT TO DO
ALL ON YOUR OWN.

402
00:23:10,458 --> 00:23:13,083
ACTUALLY, I DID HAVE
A LITTLE HELP.

403
00:23:13,125 --> 00:23:14,417
AND THERE'S
SOMETHING ELSE.

404
00:23:18,583 --> 00:23:19,417
WHAT IS IT?

405
00:23:19,458 --> 00:23:20,709
I NEED TO TALK
TO ROKU,

406
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:22,166
AND I THINK
I FOUND A WAY

407
00:23:22,208 --> 00:23:23,834
TO CONTACT
HIS SPIRIT.

408
00:23:23,875 --> 00:23:26,041
THAT'S GREAT.
CREEPY,
BUT GREAT.

409
00:23:26,083 --> 00:23:28,625
THERE'S A TEMPLE
ON A CRESCENT-SHAPED ISLAND,

410
00:23:28,667 --> 00:23:30,291
AND IF I GO THERE
ON THE SOLSTICE,

411
00:23:30,333 --> 00:23:32,166
I'LL BE ABLE
TO SPEAK WITH HIM.

412
00:23:32,208 --> 00:23:34,375
BUT THE SOLSTICE
IS TOMORROW.

413
00:23:34,417 --> 00:23:36,583
YEAH, AND THERE'S
ONE MORE PROBLEM.

414
00:23:36,625 --> 00:23:39,000
THE ISLAND
IS IN THE FIRE NATION.

415
